#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:4
msgid ""
"As well as the quantitative data gathered by users activity in the Oppia "
"app, most implementations will also want to gather qualitative data on "
"how users manage to use the Oppia app and content."
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:8
msgid ""
"Most approaches to this would use surveys, interviews and/or focus groups"
" to ask users about how they manage to use the app and ask questions such"
" as what you like/dislike about the app, or to get information about "
"specific difficulties users may be having."
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:13
msgid ""
"However, some users may be hesitant to admit they are having difficulties"
" in using the app and content, so the qualitative data might not be "
"representative."
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:16
msgid ""
"An alternative approach to asking specific questions is to give users a "
"set of short tasks to perform in the app and with the content, watching "
"the users doing the task and noting any particular issues they are "
"having."
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:20
msgid ""
"This approach is modeled on the concept of `'guerilla' usability testing "
"<https://www.slideshare.net/andybudd/guerilla-usability-testing/>`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:23
msgid "An overview of the process is:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:25
msgid "Design the tasks - each task should be specific and discrete"
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:26
msgid ""
"Introduce the project and what you are doing and why. Specifically "
"emphasise that this is about you testing the product, not the users "
"ability to complete the task"
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:29
msgid ""
"Ask the user to `think out loud "
"<https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Think_aloud_protocol>`_ as they are going "
"through each task - this gives an idea about users thought processes"
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:32
msgid ""
"Reset the device back to either the Android main screen, or the app "
"homepage, before each task"
msgstr ""

#: ../../implementers/evaluation/appui.rst:34
msgid ""
"If possible video the user whilst they are doing the task, as this is a "
"useful reference for later"
